Title: Sinner City
Actors: Tiffany Roxanne Barrett, Peedi Crakk, Tai Birch, Renee Carillo
Plot: Sinner City, a Domini Quinn SupaStar jawn. Jade Banks is at the top of her game in corporate America as C.F.O of a credit card company called Viva Express. In this satirical thriller, when Jade is unfairly passed over for a well deserved promotion, she decides to tank the company with a well devised scam called the double up. Welcome to Sinner City.
